OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FState pension payments     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstill delayed for thousands
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands of newly-retired people are  
OL,6, still yet to receive their first state 
OL,7, pension payments after a deadline for  
OL,8, backlogs in payments to be cleared.    
OL,10,FMost delayed pensions to people who    
OL,11,Fhave just turned 66 are now being paid 
OL,12,Ffollowing a catch-up exercise by the   
OL,13,FDepartment for Work and Pensions (DWP).
OL,15,FBut applications have yet to be        
OL,16,Fprocessed for 4,900 people from whom   
OL,17,Fthe DWP has asked for extra details.   
OL,19,FThe pandemic and staffing issues were  
OL,20,Fblamed for problems over the summer.   
